    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      326.72,
      543.73,
      340.72
    ],
    "text": "Heard learned Counsel for the Petitioners in support of the application for",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      347.84,
      154.85,
      361.84
    ],
    "text": "interim relief.",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      390.1,
      543.67,
      404.1
    ],
    "text": "At the very outset, this Court cannot but observe that the Petitioners have",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      411.22,
      543.9,
      425.22
    ],
    "text": "approached this Court after an inordinate and unexplained delay of exactly one",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      432.34,
      543.72,
      446.34
    ],
    "text": "year from the date of the impugned decision suspending the said students. No",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      453.48,
      543.71,
      467.48
    ],
    "text": "material has been placed before Court to satisfactorily explain such delay. The",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      474.6,
      544.0,
      488.6
    ],
    "text": "assertion that the Petitioners were unaware of the relevant examination",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      495.72,
      543.72,
      509.72
    ],
    "text": "schedule is, in the view of this Court, wholly unconvincing and unsupported by",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      516.84,
      224.71,
      530.84
    ],
    "text": "any evidence whatsoever.",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      559.11,
      543.7,
      573.11
    ],
    "text": "This Court is constrained to note that the present application has been",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      580.23,
      544.01,
      594.23
    ],
    "text": "instituted at the eleventh hour, on the eve of examinations said to be scheduled",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      601.35,
      543.68,
      615.35
    ],
    "text": "on Monday, thereby seeking to place undue pressure upon Court to grant",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      622.49,
      543.73,
      636.49
    ],
    "text": "interim relief. Such conduct is impermissible. It amounts to an attempt to",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      643.61,
      543.73,
      657.61
    ],
    "text": "invoke the writ jurisdiction of this Court in circumstances brought about solely",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      664.73,
      543.8,
      678.73
    ],
    "text": "by the Petitioners\u2019 own inaction. The writ jurisdiction, being discretionary in",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      731.62,
      123.51,
      756.1
    ],
    "text": "3 | P a g e",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      72.0,
      543.72,
      86.0
    ],
    "text": "nature, cannot be exercised in favour of litigants who have demonstrably slept",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      93.12,
      391.1,
      107.12
    ],
    "text": "on their rights and thereafter seek urgent indulgence.",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      135.39,
      543.99,
      149.39
    ],
    "text": "In the circumstances, this Court is of the firm view that the Petitioners are",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      156.51,
      543.7,
      170.51
    ],
    "text": "guilty of inordinate delay and laches, which by itself is sufficient to disentitle",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      177.63,
      543.84,
      191.63
    ],
    "text": "them to any relief, interim or otherwise. The belated challenge to the decision of",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      198.77,
      342.12,
      212.77
    ],
    "text": "the Vice Chancellor cannot be countenanced.",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      241.01,
      543.83,
      255.01
    ],
    "text": "This Court must also emphasise that matters pertaining to discipline within a",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      262.13,
      543.67,
      276.13
    ],
    "text": "university fall primarily within the domain of the Vice Chancellor and the",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      283.28,
      543.74,
      297.28
    ],
    "text": "relevant academic and administrative authorities. They are best placed, by",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      304.4,
      543.94,
      318.4
    ],
    "text": "reason of their proximity to the facts and institutional responsibility, to take",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      325.52,
      543.76,
      339.52
    ],
    "text": "decisions concerning the maintenance of discipline and order within the",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      346.64,
      543.7,
      360.64
    ],
    "text": "university. This Court, in the exercise of its writ jurisdiction, does not sit as an",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      368.02,
      543.99,
      382.02
    ],
    "text": "appellate authority over such decisions. Judicial intervention is warranted only",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      389.14,
      543.71,
      403.14
    ],
    "text": "in instances where there is a clear failure, inability, or illegality in the exercise",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      410.26,
      543.73,
      424.26
    ],
    "text": "of such powers. No such exceptional circumstance has been demonstrated in",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      431.38,
      175.75,
      445.38
    ],
    "text": "the present case.",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      473.64,
      544.01,
      487.64
    ],
    "text": "Be that as it may, this Court deems it necessary to place on record, in the",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      494.76,
      543.74,
      508.76
    ],
    "text": "clearest possible terms, that acts of ragging within university premises are",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      515.88,
      543.73,
      529.88
    ],
    "text": "matters of the gravest concern. The legislative intent underlying the Prohibition",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      537.03,
      543.72,
      551.03
    ],
    "text": "of Ragging and Other Forms of Violence in Educational Institutions Act, No. 20",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      558.15,
      543.79,
      572.15
    ],
    "text": "of 1998 is unequivocal. Enacted unanimously by Parliament, it embodies a",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      579.27,
      543.67,
      593.27
    ],
    "text": "strong national resolve to eradicate a deeply pernicious practice that has, over",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      600.39,
      397.1,
      614.39
    ],
    "text": "the years, resulted in immeasurable harm to students.",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      642.65,
      543.92,
      656.65
    ],
    "text": "This Court cannot ignore the disturbing reality that incidents of ragging have,",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      663.77,
      543.74,
      677.77
    ],
    "text": "in certain instances, allegedly driven vulnerable students to the brink of",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      684.89,
      543.71,
      698.89
    ],
    "text": "despair, even leading to tragic consequences such as the loss of life by suicide.",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      706.03,
      543.77,
      720.04
    ],
    "text": "Such allegations, whether ultimately established or not, underscore the",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      731.62,
      123.51,
      756.1
    ],
    "text": "4 | P a g e",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      72.0,
      543.71,
      86.0
    ],
    "text": "extreme gravity of the issue and the pressing need for strict enforcement of the",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      93.12,
      543.72,
      107.12
    ],
    "text": "law. Any attempt to trivialise or dilute disciplinary action taken in this regard",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      114.27,
      240.1,
      128.27
    ],
    "text": "must be firmly discouraged.",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      156.51,
      543.91,
      170.51
    ],
    "text": "Universities must remain sanctuaries of learning, dignity, and safety. The law",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
